      • rout

        private int rout(TopBaseCalResult tb)
        1. First verify the algorithm implementation under a voltage gear 2. Verify that the agp initialization is ready and get the first tb result (TopBaseCalResult) 3. Calculate the direct incremental relationship between the amplitude deviation and the parameter deviation, and study the algorithm implementation. 4. Use method combination to correct to correct under this voltage position 5. According to the incremental relationship under other voltage positions, the other conditions of the algorithm are adapted and verified one by one.
